{"type": "article", "id": 7483, "title": "花 5 万美金买一双乔丹的签名鞋，值？", "description": "据说这是最早的一双", "date": "2015-03-18T08:21:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 1900, "name": "拍卖"}, {"id": 7866, "name": "签名鞋"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 6461, "name": "乔丹"}], "category": 19, "author": 75588, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604223336suDy3SqjaKIQx9hT.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t虔诚的乔丹粉和签名鞋收藏爱好者们注意了，最早的一双乔丹穿过并赢得比赛的签名鞋下个月要开始拍卖了！不过预估价格可不低。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"img/uploads/20160604223335axb4qdgEykHXQ8Tf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t这双鞋背后还有个故事，不不，不是那些无良商家捏造出来的“背后的”故事。这双鞋属于一个叫 <span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">Khalid Ali </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的男人，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">1984 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年乔丹刚毕业进入芝加哥公牛队时，他还只有 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">15 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">岁，是洛杉矶湖人队的球童。当年 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">12 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">2 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日公牛对湖人，乔丹在做赛前热身时，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">Ali </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">走过去问乔丹能否把他的运动鞋送给自己。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t就是这么简单。<span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">2013 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年底拍卖出 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">10.4 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万美金的乔丹签名鞋，也是出自一名球童（球童的福利就在于此吧）。那双鞋来自著名的“感冒比赛”。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">1997 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年总决赛第 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">5 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">场，乔丹身患感冒坚持上场，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">44 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钟个人得分 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">38 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分：</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">7 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个篮板，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">5 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个助攻，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">3 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">次抢断，以</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\"> 90 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">比 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">88 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的略微差距拿下关键一局，最终获得总冠军。得到这双签名鞋的球童 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">Preston Truman </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">来自当时乔丹对阵的爵士队。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"img/uploads/20160604223335u4bKYRBm8G3OE5lW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.31578947\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t言归正传。日前，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">Ali </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">已委托 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">SCP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">拍卖公司处理。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">SCP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">搜寻证据，找到了当年 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">10 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">26 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日乔丹对阵太阳队时穿着这双篮球鞋的照片，湖人教练 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">Gary Vitti </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">也出具了 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">Ali </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">当时为湖人队工作的凭证。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">Ali </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">表示，这双鞋是自己在做湖人球童的岁月里最大的收获。这样的评价对湖人队而言真是不知道该说什么好。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t与之前拍出 <span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">3.1 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万美金的乔丹作为新人参赛的签名鞋相比，这双鞋更具有不同的意义。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">Ali </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">拿到这双篮球鞋后三个月，乔丹一代上市。当时售价 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">65 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">美金一双，仅两个月销售额便达到了七千万美元。耐克花重金（比当时的顶级球星还要贵五倍）与其签约，总算也是名利双收。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t好了，了解完这双鞋的意义，可以决定要不要去<a href=\"scpauctions.com\" target=\"_blank\">拍卖网站</a><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">掺一脚了。不过要知道，近些年愿意为乔丹的比赛签名鞋花大价钱的大有人在，拍卖公司预估这双鞋能拍到 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">5 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万美金左右。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t图片来源：SCP 拍卖公司 \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}